{"tid":700452,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中原料今年樓價升17%　即使有空置稅亦不改樓市升勢","createTime":"2018-06-13T10:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T04:38:32.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56e0d008dc2d6659b0afebbb5f32fa7da824c536","tid":700452,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"中原料今年樓價升17%　即使有空置稅亦不改樓市升勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1401482_1_20180613151432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1401482_1_20180613151432.jpg&h=8b8d58f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中原地產預料，今年樓價升17%，即使推出一手物業空置稅亦不會改變樓市升勢。</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中原地產表示，經濟上升支持樓價持續向上，加息反映經濟增長，將有利樓市再創新高，預料今年樓價升17%，即使推出一手物業空置稅亦不會改變樓市升勢。<br />\n<br />\n中原預計，一手私人住宅貨尾將逐漸減少，估計今年一手樓銷售宗數2萬宗，按年升8.1%，創14年新高；銷售金額亦升7%至2600億元，連續兩年創新高。<br />\n<br />\n中原又估計，今年二手私人住宅銷售達4萬宗，按年升0.6%，銷售金額達3000億元，按年微升0.4%，但創6年新高。<br />\n<br />\n中原預期，包括工商舖、住宅及車位等，今年整體樓宇買賣金額8000億元，按年升10.1%，創21年新高。買賣宗數9萬宗，按年升7.4%。"},{"pid":"39bfd15e24f05e83da21c523dcbfde763644d690","tid":700452,"uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"宇宙間再無任何野可以阻止香港樓價上升。"},{"pid":"aa902821cce28c0e861ea7b28206d961c45653a3","tid":700452,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39bfd15e24f05e83da21c523dcbfde763644d690","tid":700452,"uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"宇宙間再無任何野可以阻止香港樓價上升。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},